text: The Dalvik Church () is a church building at Dalvik in the town of Jönköping in Sweden. It is a Swedish Evangelical Mission church. It belongs to the Jönköping Sofia-Järstorp Parish of the Swedish Evangelical Mission. It was inaugurated on 8 February 1969 and expanded in 1985. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Church of Sweden churches Category:Buildings and structures in Jönköping
title: Dalvik Church
